<Link id="l00627" /><CodeLine lineNumber="627"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00628" /><CodeLine lineNumber="628"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// Get the size of the note, including name, descriptor, and padding. Both</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00629" /><CodeLine lineNumber="629"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// the start and the end of the descriptor are aligned by the section</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00630" /><CodeLine lineNumber="630"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// alignment. In practice many 64-bit systems deviate from the generic ABI by</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00631" /><CodeLine lineNumber="631"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// using sh&#95;addralign=4.</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00701" /><CodeLine lineNumber="701"><span class="doxyHighlight">    &#42;Err = <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a9999bd897fc8a1648bd69b36fee2d357">make&#95;error&lt;StringError&gt;</a>(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;ELF note overflows container&quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">,</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00705" /><CodeLine lineNumber="705"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Advance Nhdr by NoteSize bytes, starting from NhdrPos.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00706" /><CodeLine lineNumber="706"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00707" /><CodeLine lineNumber="707"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Assumes NoteSize &lt;= RemainingSize. Ensures Nhdr-&gt;getSize() &lt;= RemainingSize</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00708" /><CodeLine lineNumber="708"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// upon returning. Handles stopping iteration when reaching the end of the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00709" /><CodeLine lineNumber="709"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// container, either cleanly or with an overflow error.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00710" /><CodeLine lineNumber="710"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">void</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> advanceNhdr(</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> uint8&#95;t &#42;NhdrPos, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">size&#95;t</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> NoteSize) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00711" /><CodeLine lineNumber="711"><span class="doxyHighlight">    RemainingSize -= NoteSize;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00712" /><CodeLine lineNumber="712"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (RemainingSize == 0u) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00713" /><CodeLine lineNumber="713"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Ensure that if the iterator walks to the end, the error is checked</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00714" /><CodeLine lineNumber="714"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// afterwards.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00715" /><CodeLine lineNumber="715"><span class="doxyHighlight">      &#42;Err = <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error/#a4dfd0813c3d0e0a30439b5a3e9196b59">Error::success</a>();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00716" /><CodeLine lineNumber="716"><span class="doxyHighlight">      Nhdr = </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">nullptr</span><span class="doxyHighlight">;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00717" /><CodeLine lineNumber="717"><span class="doxyHighlight">    &#125; </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">sizeof</span><span class="doxyHighlight">(&#42;Nhdr) &gt; RemainingSize)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00718" /><CodeLine lineNumber="718"><span class="doxyHighlight">      stopWithOverflowError();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00719" /><CodeLine lineNumber="719"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00720" /><CodeLine lineNumber="720"><span class="doxyHighlight">      Nhdr = </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">reinterpret&#95;cast&lt;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const </span><span class="doxyHighlight">Elf&#95;Nhdr&#95;Impl&lt;ELFT&gt; &#42;</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">&gt;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">(NhdrPos + NoteSize);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00721" /><CodeLine lineNumber="721"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Nhdr-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/object/elf-nhdr-impl/#a3a8d45f58be1922403c4d098c8c65eeb">getSize</a>(<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/align">Align</a>) &gt; RemainingSize)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00722" /><CodeLine lineNumber="722"><span class="doxyHighlight">        stopWithOverflowError();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00723" /><CodeLine lineNumber="723"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00724" /><CodeLine lineNumber="724"><span class="doxyHighlight">        &#42;Err = <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error/#a4dfd0813c3d0e0a30439b5a3e9196b59">Error::success</a>();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00725" /><CodeLine lineNumber="725"><span class="doxyHighlight">    &#125;</span></CodeLine>
